  <brief_title>Vibration Training in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD)-Patients During a Three-week Rehabilitation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Whole Body Vibration Training on Physical Activity in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) III/IV-Patients During a Three-week Rehabilitation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
