  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate the change of physical activity in COPD-patients
      performing a whole body vibration training additional to a standard three-week rehabilitation
      program in comparison to patients performing merely a standard rehabilitation program.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
